Maze

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • Maze.Tile
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoorTile, ExitTile, FreeTile, GateTile, InfoTile, WallTile

    public abstract class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class representing a tile in the game. This abstract class is extended by concrete classes like DoorTile, ExitTile etc. The board is made up of tiles (with items on some of the tiles).
